JOB SUMMARY:
• Be in charge of marketing execution;
• Arrange trip, event, promotion & sales support activities for the Company.

KEY RESPONSIBILITIES & TASKS:
1. Marketing duties (55%)
a. Plan, develop and execute MKT activity plans;
b. Prepare and monitor the marketing budget on a job basis and allocate funds wisely;
c. Liaise with graphic designer to create marketing tools (backdrop, standee, leaflet, brochure…), marketing campaign under Marketing Manager’s assignments;
d. Develop content of website, social media, newsletter, owned-media channels, etc.
e. Coordinate with Compliance team to prepare documents for license registering with Authorities;
f. Work closely with Customers to support them, get their ideas, comments about company’s promotion programs, sales/ training tools.
2. Trips promotion duties (25%)
a. Handle registration process of BAs participating in the trip promotion program;
b. Support/ arrange for visas, book flights, etc. for qualified BAs to attend overseas trips/ events.
c. Be in charge of all trip related jobs as assigned by line manager.

3. Event duties (15%)
a. Propose and plan for marketing campaign, events, conferences, camp, etc.
b. Search for vendors with quality and efficient cost;
c. Manage all event operations (preparing venue, set up, event running, etc.);
d. Manage and follow up with contract and payment.

